name: Little Fairy Xiao-Dan / 晓丹小仙女
description:
Introduction

Little Fairy Xiao-dan is a popular internet celebrity on Bilibili and Douyin, two Chinese video platforms. She mainly imitates anime characters and ancient Chinese beauties, with a cute, fresh and aesthetic style. Her Bilibili account is Xiaodan Xiaoxiannv, and her Douyin ID is xiaodanXXN. Her video works are very popular, and some of them are reposted to other platforms.
